<td tEditID="c1r2" style=" background-color:#FFFFFF; color:#000000; bEditID:r3st1; bLabel:main; font-size:12pt; font-family:arial;" aEditID="c1r2" locked="0" >
<![CDATA[<font face="Arial" size="2" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="line-height: 17.94px; white-space: pre-wrap;">Dear {!Contact.FirstName},</span></font><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><font face="Arial" size="2"><span style="line-height: 17.94px; white-space: pre-wrap;"><br></span></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><font face="Arial" size="2"><span style="line-height: 17.94px; white-space: pre-wrap;">We hope you've been keeping well!</span></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><font face="Arial" size="2"><span style="line-height: 17.94px; white-space: pre-wrap;"><br></span></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><font face="Arial" size="2"><span style="line-height: 17.94px; white-space: pre-wrap;">Applications to work on the NCS programme this summer are currently open, and we'd love for you to join us again and bring back your expertise, enthusiasm and experience.</span></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><font face="Arial" size="2"><span style="line-height: 17.94px; white-space: pre-wrap;"><br></span></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><font face="Arial" size="2"><span style="line-height: 17.94px; white-space: pre-wrap;">We count on our brilliant alumni to help us keep each NCS programme to the same high standard as the last. This year, we're recruiting more than 4,500 seasonal roles, across more locations than ever before. NCS is growing, and we want you to be a part of it.</span></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><font face="Arial" size="2"><span style="line-height: 17.94px; white-space: pre-wrap;"><br></span></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><font face="Arial" size="2"><span style="line-height: 17.94px; white-space: pre-wrap;"><b>Why should you come back to us?</b></span></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><font face="Arial" size="2"><span style="line-height: 17.94px; white-space: pre-wrap;"><b><br></b></span></font></div><div><ul><li><font face="Arial" size="2"><span style="line-height: 17.94px; white-space: pre-wrap;"><b>New locations: </b>we've expanded and are now providing NCS in Leeds &amp; Bradford, Surrey, and Buckinghamshire &amp; Berkshire, as well as in Greater London, the West Midlands and North-West England.</span></font></li></ul></div><div><ul><li><font face="Arial" size="2"><span style="line-height: 17.94px; white-space: pre-wrap;"><b>New roles: </b>we've got new inclusion roles which focus on making the NCS programme accessible to even more young people. If your experience lies in supporting people with additional needs or challenging behaviour, these roles are for you. If working 1-2-1 with a young person isn't your thing, we've still got a range of leader, mentor and specialist roles for you to choose from - <a href="http://www.ncsthechallenge.org/jobs/#available-opportunities">click here to find out more!</a></span></font></li></ul></div><div><ul><li><font face="Arial" size="2"><b>No assessment: </b>as a member of our valued alumni, we know that you're an excellent candidate for our roles. That means that if you're joining us again in the same role as before, you'll be provisionally offered a role straight away, without needing to attend another assessment.</font></li></ul></div><div><ul><li><font face="Arial" size="2"><b>New 'returner' training: </b>if you're taking on the same roles as before you'll only have to attend one day of returner training to refresh your memory, rather than the full 2-3 days like before!</font></li></ul><div><font face="Arial" size="2"><br></font></div></div><div><font face="Arial" size="2"><b>Sounds great! What do I need to do?</b></font></div><div><font face="Arial" size="2"><b><br></b></font></div><div><font face="Arial" size="2">To apply to work with us again, you just need to log in to the staffing website using the same login-details as before - if you can't remember your password (it has been a while, after all), you can use the 'forgotten password' option to retrieve it.</font></div><div><font face="Arial" size="2"><br></font></div><div><font face="Arial" size="2">Then you'll be able to check your details on 'My Profile' are still correct, and then head onto the 'My Application' page.</font></div><div><font face="Arial" size="2"><br></font></div><div><font face="Arial" size="2"><br></font></div><div style="text-align: center;"><font face="Arial" size="2"><a href="https://staffing.the-challenge.org/Login.aspx">Click here to login to the staffing website!</a></font></div><div style="text-align: center;"><br></div><div style="text-align: center;"><br></div><div style="text-align: left;"><b><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">Any questions?</font></b></div><div style="text-align: left;"><b><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><br></font></b></div><div style="text-align: left;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">We know a lot has changed since we last worked with you, so if you need to refresh your memory, or find out more about NCS in 2016, please see our <u><a href="https://staffing.the-challenge.org/frequently-asked-questions/">FAQs</a></u>. You can also contact us on <u><font color="#3366ff">seasonalroles@the-challenge.org</font></u> to get any questions you have answered!</font></div><div style="text-align: left;"><br></div><div style="text-align: left;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">We hope to receive an application from you soon!</font></div><div style="text-align: left;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><br></font></div><div style="text-align: left;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><br></font></div><div style="text-align: left;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">Best wishes,</font></div><div style="text-align: left;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><br></font></div><div style="text-align: left;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">The Staffing Team</font></div><div style="text-align: left;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">The Challenge</font></div><div style="text-align: left;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2" color="#3366ff"><u>seasonalroles@the-challenge.org</u></font></div><div><font face="Arial" size="2"><br></font></div>]]></td>
</tr>
